    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We try to push as much as possible functionality outside of core IPython. We will even split the widget into its own repo soon after the release of IPython 3.0. So widget are limited (by design) to really minimal expressions. \n\nSo I doubt something like that will ever be in core, and we encourage you and everyone else to developp library that rely on widgets, and provide higher-level abstraction. \n"
